51:54.695 --> 51:56.963
- Thank you, Lord Risley.
- The King is saved
from conspirators.

51:57.064 --> 51:59.031
And Anne Askew...

51:59.099 --> 52:01.233
- Sweetheart?

52:01.334 --> 52:04.502
I hear you've been busying
yourself with your books.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

52:04.570 --> 52:08.673
I have translated works
by Erasmus,

52:08.774 --> 52:10.842
as well as buying
a beautiful book of psalms

52:10.909 --> 52:13.411
by Thomas Berthelet.

52:13.512 --> 52:16.047
- I wonder, Kate,

52:16.114 --> 52:18.015
at your diligence.

52:18.083 --> 52:20.852
- Well, I regard it as much
my duty as my pleasure,

52:20.953 --> 52:24.590
to place such wonderful books

52:24.691 --> 52:27.026
before the good English people
who have been a long time

52:27.094 --> 52:30.063
thirsting and hungering
for the sincere

52:30.164 --> 52:32.399
and plain knowledge
of God's Word.

52:32.467 --> 52:34.501
- Just be cautious.

52:34.569 --> 52:37.404
Not every English person can
read or understand the Gospels.

52:37.472 --> 52:39.406
And you are to be careful

52:39.507 --> 52:41.508
of the consequences
of encouraging them to try.

52:41.609 --> 52:43.510
- Majesty, I am not afraid
of the Gospels,

52:43.611 --> 52:45.845
nor should anyone be afraid.

52:47.915 --> 52:50.682
Your Majesty has begun
a great work in banishing

52:50.783 --> 52:53.218
the monstrous idol of Rome.

52:53.286 --> 52:55.220
And now with God's help,

52:55.288 --> 52:57.623
you can finish that work

52:57.691 --> 53:00.760
by purging the Church of England
of its dregs.

53:18.045 --> 53:20.947
Majesty...
- Forgive me. I am tired.

53:35.562 --> 53:38.231
- Majesty.

53:38.299 --> 53:41.434
Kate.

53:49.008 --> 53:51.242
- Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

53:52.878 --> 53:54.980
- Majesty.
- Majesty.

53:55.047 --> 53:56.915
- Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

53:57.016 --> 53:59.817
- Your Majesty.

53:59.918 --> 54:01.919
- What a thing it is,

54:01.986 --> 54:05.288
when women become such clerks,

54:05.389 --> 54:07.723
and what a comfort it will
be to me in my old age

54:07.825 --> 54:10.793
to be lectured to by my wife.

54:10.861 --> 54:13.562
- Your Majesty has no need
to be taught by anyone.

54:15.732 --> 54:18.268
Your knowledge of divinity
excels that of the princes

54:18.335 --> 54:21.371
and divines
throughout the ages.

54:23.641 --> 54:28.179
Forgive me, but I think
it unseemly for any

54:28.280 --> 54:32.117
of your subjects
to argue with you,

54:32.218 --> 54:36.121
as the Queen has
just done. Majesty,

54:36.222 --> 54:39.391
many of the greatest
subjects in the land

54:39.492 --> 54:43.361
defending those same arguments
that she does

54:43.428 --> 54:46.931
have, by law, deserved death.

54:47.032 --> 54:49.900
- I cannot believe

54:49.968 --> 54:52.836
that you would accuse the Queen
of heresy without proof.

54:52.903 --> 54:57.741
- I have the proof.
But what I need

54:57.842 --> 55:00.945
is Your Majesty's consent
to draw up certain articles

55:01.046 --> 55:04.482
against the Queen, so that
she may be put on trial.

55:12.091 --> 55:15.761
- She could be put
on trial. And yet,

55:15.829 --> 55:18.998
I am fully resolved
to spare her life.

55:19.065 --> 55:21.267
- Certainly.

55:21.368 --> 55:25.138
Whatever Your Majesty desires.

